Mass Spectrometry Data Backend for MassBank Files

The MsBackendMassbank package provides functionality to import and handle MS/MS spectrum data from Massbank files. The package defines the MsBackendMassbank backend which can be used to import and use MS2 spectrum data from mgf files with the Spectra R package.

For more information see the package homepage.
